{"id":"xhs_traffic_no_revenue","user_message":"我做小红书半年有 3000 粉丝，但没有收入，是不是继续发就会起来？","intent":"diagnose content-to-revenue failure","stage":"validation","must_include":["business_judgment","case_or_pattern","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","china_reality_or_constraint","next_action","stop_loss"],"must_avoid":["持续输出","打造个人品牌","多发爆款","先涨粉","坚持下去"],"scoring_focus":["business_essence","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","china_reality","execution_friction","expression_quality"],"pass_bar":"必须指出粉丝不是收入资产，核心断点是付费场景和承接链路；必须给出直接竞品或路径对标、收费机制和证据边界；要给出一个低阻力验证动作，例如用 3 条笔记引导私信诊断或低价资料包，并写清停损信号。"}
{"id":"icp_before_validation","user_message":"我想做一个 SaaS 官网，是不是应该先买大陆服务器备案，显得正规一点？","intent":"avoid premature compliance work","stage":"validation","must_include":["business_judgment","case_or_pattern","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","china_reality_or_constraint","next_action","stop_loss"],"must_avoid":["建议备案","先做官网","提高品牌形象","搭建完整网站","长期主义"],"scoring_focus":["china_reality","business_essence","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","execution_friction"],"pass_bar":"必须讲清备案和香港/新加坡服务器的权衡：早期验证先降低摩擦，长期品牌和小程序生态再考虑主体与备案；必须说明直接竞品或替代承接页、收费机制和证据边界，并把官网从信任问题拉回成交验证问题。"}
{"id":"ai_topic_tool_generic","user_message":"我想做一个 AI 小红书选题助手，帮博主生成标题和笔记方向，这个能不能做？","intent":"judge AI content tool idea","stage":"idea","must_include":["business_judgment","case_or_pattern","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","china_reality_or_constraint","next_action","stop_loss"],"must_avoid":["做 MVP","找到痛点","持续优化模型","提高生成质量","差异化"],"scoring_focus":["case_or_pattern","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","business_essence","platform_risk","next_action"],"pass_bar":"必须指出泛内容生成工具价值低，机会在具体人群和结果承诺；必须区分直接竞品、相邻替代、免费替代，说明收费机制和证据边界；要给出手工交付 3 个真实账号选题方案的验证动作。"}
{"id":"one_person_10k_goal","user_message":"我现在每月只想赚 1 万，应该选 SaaS、知识付费还是自媒体？","intent":"choose route by constraint not preference","stage":"idea","must_include":["business_judgment","case_or_pattern","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","china_reality_or_constraint","next_action","stop_loss"],"must_avoid":["看你兴趣","都可以尝试","长期积累","先做内容","选择适合自己的"],"scoring_focus":["route_planning","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","business_essence","execution_friction"],"pass_bar":"必须先用 1 万/月这个目标反推现金流路径，通常应优先服务/咨询/资料包而不是重 SaaS；必须给出直接竞品或路线对标、收费机制和证据边界，说明三条路线的代价，并给出本周能收第一笔钱的动作。"}
{"id":"developer_no_sales","user_message":"我有技术能力，但不会社交和销售，怎么做一人公司？","intent":"translate capability gap into distribution design","stage":"idea","must_include":["business_judgment","case_or_pattern","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","china_reality_or_constraint","next_action","stop_loss"],"must_avoid":["学习销售","打造影响力","多交流","做开源","坚持输出"],"scoring_focus":["distribution","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","execution_friction","case_or_pattern"],"pass_bar":"必须指出技术不是短板，缺的是可重复触达付费用户的渠道；必须给出直接竞品或路径对标、收费机制和证据边界；要给出适合内向技术人的插件/模板/API/垂直工具路线，并要求用公开问题和付费预售验证。"}
{"id":"ai_automation_service_outsourcing","user_message":"我想做 AI 自动化服务，帮企业把流程自动化，但怕最后变成外包，怎么办？","intent":"avoid service trap","stage":"first_revenue","must_include":["business_judgment","case_or_pattern","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","china_reality_or_constraint","next_action","stop_loss"],"must_avoid":["标准化服务","沉淀 SOP","提高交付效率","做成产品","积累案例"],"scoring_focus":["delivery_model","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","pricing","stop_loss"],"pass_bar":"必须区分项目外包、产品化服务和 SaaS 的边界，指出外包化的信号；必须给出直接竞品或服务对标、收费机制和证据边界；要给出固定范围、固定价格、固定输入输出的试单设计，并写清超过几次定制就停。"}
{"id":"paid_newsletter_china","user_message":"我想做一个面向国内独立开发者的付费 newsletter，有机会吗？","intent":"evaluate paid media business in China context","stage":"idea","must_include":["business_judgment","case_or_pattern","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","china_reality_or_constraint","next_action","stop_loss"],"must_avoid":["坚持写","做个人品牌","先积累读者","提高内容质量","长期主义"],"scoring_focus":["case_or_pattern","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","china_reality","monetization"],"pass_bar":"必须说明付费 newsletter 在本土支付习惯、平台承接和信任上的问题；必须给出直接竞品或相邻替代、收费机制和证据边界；要把机会落到具体付费信息差或决策节省。"}
{"id":"notion_site_builder_cn","user_message":"我想做一个 Notion 建站工具，给国内一人公司快速做官网，这个方向怎么样？","intent":"evaluate platform-layer product","stage":"idea","must_include":["business_judgment","case_or_pattern","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","china_reality_or_constraint","next_action","stop_loss"],"must_avoid":["做模板","提高易用性","先开发","满足建站需求","做差异化"],"scoring_focus":["case_or_pattern","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","platform_dependency","china_reality"],"pass_bar":"必须指出 Notion 在访问、备案、信任和微信生态承接的问题；必须用 Feather/Potion/Bullet 等直接竞品或相邻替代做对标，说明收费机制和证据边界，并判断它更像临时验证页而非长期官网。"}
{"id":"knowledge_product_pricing","user_message":"我做了一个一人公司避坑手册，应该卖 99 还是 199？","intent":"price by buyer and promise","stage":"first_revenue","must_include":["business_judgment","case_or_pattern","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","china_reality_or_constraint","next_action","stop_loss"],"must_avoid":["看用户接受度","做 A/B 测试","提高价值感","都可以","先低价"],"scoring_focus":["pricing","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","offer_design","next_action"],"pass_bar":"必须指出价格不是数字选择，而是承诺和买家筛选；必须给出直接竞品或替代付费内容、收费机制和证据边界；要给出 99/199 分别对应的交付边界，并要求先卖给 10 个具体用户看支付和退款理由。"}
{"id":"mini_program_vs_web","user_message":"我想做小程序，会不会比网页更适合国内用户？","intent":"choose channel by transaction path","stage":"validation","must_include":["business_judgment","case_or_pattern","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","china_reality_or_constraint","next_action","stop_loss"],"must_avoid":["小程序用户体验好","国内用户习惯微信","都做一个","看目标用户","先开发版本"],"scoring_focus":["china_reality","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","execution_friction","route_planning"],"pass_bar":"必须讲清小程序的主体、审核、支付、分享和微信生态优势，同时指出早期验证可能被开发和审核拖慢；必须给出直接竞品或渠道替代、收费机制和证据边界，并给出低成本承接页/私域试单优先的判断。"}
{"id":"prompt_product_opportunity","user_message":"我想卖提示词或智能体，这个方向还有机会吗？","intent":"evaluate commoditized AI product","stage":"idea","must_include":["business_judgment","case_or_pattern","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","china_reality_or_constraint","next_action","stop_loss"],"must_avoid":["提示词工程很重要","包装成课程","做社群","持续更新","抓住 AI 红利"],"scoring_focus":["business_essence","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","commoditization","offer_design"],"pass_bar":"必须指出提示词本身很难成为护城河，机会在垂直场景、私有数据、交付结果或工作流；必须给出直接竞品或免费替代、收费机制和证据边界，并给出把提示词藏在服务/工具背后的验证方式。"}
{"id":"too_many_features_no_payment","user_message":"我做了很多功能，但用户就是不付费，是不是还缺一个关键功能？","intent":"diagnose feature trap","stage":"validation","must_include":["business_judgment","case_or_pattern","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","china_reality_or_constraint","next_action","stop_loss"],"must_avoid":["继续迭代","收集反馈","优化体验","增加核心功能","提高留存"],"scoring_focus":["business_essence","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","stop_loss","next_action"],"pass_bar":"必须指出功能不是问题，缺的是付费理由或高频付费场景；必须给出直接竞品或简单产品对标、收费机制和证据边界；要要求删到一个付费动作，用预售或手工交付验证，并给出连续 10 个目标用户不付费就暂停开发的停损线。"}
{"id":"markdown_to_html_product_judgment","user_message":"/产品判断 我想做一个 markdown 转 html 的产品","intent":"judge a small conversion tool with market and payment mechanisms","stage":"idea","must_include":["business_judgment","case_or_pattern","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","china_reality_or_constraint","next_action","stop_loss"],"must_avoid":["这不是产品","只是功能","没人会付费","找10个人问问","先做MVP"],"scoring_focus":["market_mapping","competitor_layering","payment_mechanism","evidence_boundary","competitor_pattern","business_essence","next_action"],"pass_bar":"必须承认转换工具可以收费，但要拆清楚具体付费场景：直接竞品、相邻替代、免费替代或高价替代，它们靠什么收费机制收费，证据边界是什么，用户为什么现在付钱，markdown 转 html 的可收费切口在哪里；不能只说这是功能不是生意。"}
